OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,FA #450,000 initiative to explore
OL,6,Fsolutions to tackle the blue-green
OL,7,Falgae crisis at Lough Neagh has been
OL,8,Flaunched.
OL,10,FEnvironment minister Andrew Muir said
OL,11,Fhe hoped solutions could also be
OL,12,Fapplied in other areas affected by the
OL,13,Fnoxious blooms.
OL,15,FIn phase one of the Lough Neagh: Blue-
OL,16,FGreen Algae Small Business Research
OL,17,FInitiative (SBRI) five applicants will
OL,18,Fbe selected to develop concepts to
OL,19,Fdeal with the algae.
