OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,FIn phase two two to three concepts
OL,6,Fwill be selected and developed as
OL,7,Fpotential pilot solutions.
OL,9,FNoxious blooms of blue-green algae
OL,10,Fcovered large parts of the lough last
OL,11,Fsummer and also affected other
OL,12,Fwaterways and beaches in the region.
OL,14,FThe algae has returned this year.
OL,16,FLough Neagh, the biggest freshwater
OL,17,Flake by surface area in the UK and
OL,18,FIreland, supplies 40% of Northern
OL,19,FIreland's drinking water and sustains
OL,20,Fa major eel-fishing industry.
