OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,FThe Stormont Executive approved its
OL,6,FLough Neagh Action Plan last month.
OL,8,FMr Muir said: "We all have a
OL,9,Fresponsibility to work collectively to
OL,10,Fdeliver sustainable solutions to
OL,11,Faddress the issues facing Lough Neagh
OL,12,Fand to return it to its rightful state
OL,13,Fas an ecological jewel at the heart of
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland.
