OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,F"I understand that this SBRI
OL,6,Finitiative will not fully address the
OL,7,Fblue-green algae problems, however it
OL,8,Fwill contribute, along with the other
OL,9,Factions contained in the Lough Neagh
OL,10,Freport, to help deliver my vision to
OL,11,Fhave a healthy, resilient environment
OL,12,Fwith high water quality status and
OL,13,Fenvironment standards thereby
OL,14,Fcontributing to the health and
OL,15,Fwellbeing of our citizens."
