OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,FHe added: "Whilst much attention has
OL,6,Fbeen devoted to the issues with blue-
OL,7,Fgreen algae in Lough Neagh I am
OL,8,Fequally focused on water quality
OL,9,Fissues across Northern Ireland and
OL,10,Fthis work will hopefully provide
OL,11,Fsolutions that can be applied to any
OL,12,Farea that has been affected by the
OL,13,Femergence of blue-green algae."
OL,15,FThe scheme is being partly funded by
OL,16,FStormont's Department for the Economy.
