OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,FEconomy Minister Conor Murphy said:
OL,6,F"There is scope for physical, chemical
OL,7,For biological, or a combination of
OL,8,Fsolutions, but whatever solution is
OL,9,Fdeveloped it must not contribute to
OL,10,Ffurther environmental degradation. It
OL,11,Fmust also comply with legislation and
OL,12,Fenvironmental designations."
OL,14,FThe application window for phase one
OL,15,Fis open for six weeks. Applications
OL,16,Fmust be received by 3pm on Friday
OL,17,FSeptember 13.
