OL,3,CHow to solve NI's toxic algae problem
OL,5,FIt is anticipated that phase one will
OL,6,Frun to March 2025 with a potential
OL,7,Fcall for a phase two applications
OL,8,Fbeginning summer 2025.
OL,10,FNitrogen and phosphorus from
OL,11,Fagricultural fertiliser running off
OL,12,Ffields is believed to be a major
OL,13,Fcontributory factor in the blue-green
OL,14,Falgae blooms.
OL,16,FThe spread of the invasive zebra
OL,17,Fmussel species is also understood to
OL,18,Fhave played a role in the blooms, as
OL,19,Fthey have made the water clearer,
OL,20,Fallowing more sunlight to penetrate,
OL,21,Fstimulating more algal photosynthesis.
